  <brief_title>Amlodipine vs Nitrates Study in Patients With Chronic Stable Angina</brief_title>
  <acronym>ANISSA</acronym>
  <official_title>Open Label Study Comparing Amlodipine vs Long-Acting Nitrates in Patients With Chronic Stable Angina.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Pfizer</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Pfizer</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of study is to compare the anti-ischemic efficacy and safety profiles of once
      daily amlodipine or isosorbide-5-mononitrate in the treatment of stable asymptomatic and
      symptomatic myocardial ischemia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
